\n譚日旭指立國歌法無可厚非。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:42:15.000Z","msg":"無厚非, 即係有 &quot;薄&quot; 非 ?"},{"pid":"eaf043b7a82c8b89f23ea466df03dd10be51dcbb","tid":684791,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f5028a3d046e21183757c58484bf1fbec396f6a","tid":684791,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"181ce3b1bbc5003d1f98593e6159b77f92142c67","tid":684791,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bface8990baa52583259a828dcda330bbc8409e2","tid":684791,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:08:22.000Z","msg":"支持校長"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180326/s00011/1521999043260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180326%2Fs00011%2F1521999043260&d=7XoLXWbv7emJM5%2BbI3wmLYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=50ede076\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180326%2Fs00011%2F1521999043260&h=f0449673\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180326/s00011/1521999043260</a><br />\n<br />\n譚日旭指立國歌法無可厚非。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:42:15.000Z","msg":"無厚非, 即係有 &quot;薄&quot; 非 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:53:06.000Z","msg":"搵到成段文, 證明譚日旭校長真係好本土<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/News/20180326/hk-gfa2_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20180326%2Fhk-gfa2_r.htm&d=7XoLXWbv7emJM5%2BbI3wmLYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0e366d92\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/News/20180326/hk-gfa2_r.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n對於政府近日公布《國歌法》本地立法，提出在中小學內教授國歌，譚日旭認同應對國歌有所認識，「我們現在都有教的，國歌我覺得應該要教的，一個國家的國歌你都不認識，那你作為一個國民，都不是很合理」，故譚日旭指立國歌法無可厚非。<br />\n<br />\n應教國歌 國民不懂不合理<br />\n<br />\n<strong>譚日旭認為大家不可能否認自己是中國人，「有些年輕人的講法，甚至香港有些成年人都是這樣教導，指『我是香港人，不是中國人』。我不會認同這樣的。</strong>你是中國人就是中國人」。譚感嘆現今香港欠家國觀念，「無國怎有家呢？你回看中國100年前被外國人欺負的時候，我們早一兩代人那樣的淒慘」，又指「港獨」天方夜譚，「我們屬於中國的一部分，我們的食物、水、電力，起碼一部分來自中國」，認為香港沒條件談港獨。"},{"pid":"f0caeb6bc839d679bcbafda4dd94d8f43ff5f752","tid":684791,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}